<section class="page-head">
  <h1>Market News</h1>
  <p>Reliable market news and research links for Australian and international shares. These are external sources, not financial advice.</p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Recommended sources</h2>
  <p class="hint">Use official announcements first, then compare market commentary across several sources before making a sandbox decision.</p>

  <div class="grid two news-source-grid">
    <div class="card inner news-source-box">
      <h3>Official ASX information</h3>
      <p>Best for company announcements, price-sensitive notices, market updates and official exchange information.</p>
      <div class="actions wrap">
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.asx.com.au/markets/trade-our-cash-market/todays-announcements" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Today's ASX announcements</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.asx.com.au/markets/trade-our-cash-market/announcements" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ASX announcement search</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.asx.com.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ASX market wrap</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card inner news-source-box">
      <h3>Australian market summaries</h3>
      <p>Best for quick ASX summaries, sector movement, market movers and company-level context.</p>
      <div class="actions wrap">
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.marketindex.com.au/news" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Market Index news</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.morningstar.com.au/market/australia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Morningstar Australia markets</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.commsec.com.au/market-news.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CommSec market news</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card inner news-source-box">
      <h3>Global market news</h3>
      <p>Best for international context, Wall Street, macroeconomic news and global market sentiment.</p>
      <div class="actions wrap">
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.reuters.com/markets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reuters markets</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.reuters.com/markets/stocks/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reuters stock markets</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://finance.yahoo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Yahoo Finance</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card inner news-source-box">
      <h3>Research and education</h3>
      <p>Best for deeper explanations, valuation, ETFs, dividend context and long-term investor education.</p>
      <div class="actions wrap">
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.morningstar.com.au/insights/stocks" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Morningstar stock insights</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.livewiremarkets.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Livewire Markets</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://www.rba.gov.au/media-releases/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">RBA releases</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

